b"ConAgra CEO on CNBC: Over the last couple of quarters, they've seen digital up 100%. They reach them on their phones and are being delivered to homes or curbside pick-up. All their customers are involved in it now. $CAG $BGS"

b'ConAgra CEO on CNBC: We are experiencing an acceleration of product trial that normally would take years. Once they\'ve tried the "new" products like cauliflower tater tots, they keep buying it. Without the pandemic, would never have even tried that product. $CAG $BGS'
